tooltipText: Your spells cannot be interrupted. Damage and healing spells are 30% more potent. Additionally, 50% all overhealing from your basic healing spells is converted into health shield on the target, up to a maximum of 30% of their maximum health. Consume up to 3 Divine Power charges, increases duration by 2 seconds per charge consumed. Instant cast, long cooldown.
name: Cleric_DivineConcentration
